             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prisoner is my apprentice; I have known him ever since he was five years old; he always behaved very honest and just, as a servant should do; he has been trusted with a great deal of property; he never wronged man, woman, nor child; he is a <rs id="t17781021-11-deflabel64" type="occupation">chimney-sweeper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17781021-11-defend130 t17781021-11-deflabel64"></join>.</p>
